<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark">
  <title>Document</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    .intimation {
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      color: white;
      padding-left: 140px;
      padding-right: 140px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18px;
    }

    .message {
      padding-left: 76px;
      padding-right: 71px;
      text-align: left;
      color: white;
      font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 12px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18px;
    }

    .button {
      width: 120px;
      height: 30px;
      background-color: rgba(253, 147, 32, 0.8);
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: none;
      margin-top: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: white;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {

      .intimation,
      .message {
        padding-left: 12%;
        padding-right: 12%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div
    style="width:100%;padding:0;margin:0;box-sizing:border-box;background: #033348;padding:2% 4%;padding-bottom: 4%;">
    <img style="height: 60px;width: 60px;padding-left:4%;margin-top:1%;margin-bottom:1.5%;"
      src="https://mittarvtesting.blob.core.windows.net/mittarv-icons/mittarv_logo_white_tm.png" />

    <div
      style="background: #054A68;padding:2% 4%;margin-bottom:2%;border-radius: 5px;text-align: center;">
      <img style="margin-top:40px;margin-bottom:1.5%; width: 51px; height: 50px;"
        src="https://mittarvtesting.blob.core.windows.net/mittarv-icons/ew_miss_you_1.png" />
      <h2
        style="color:white;font-weight:700;font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1.5%; text-align: center;">
        We Miss You!</h2>
      <h2
        style="color:white;font-weight:700;font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1.5%; text-align: center;">
        Come back and continue building <br /> your legacy.</h2>
      <p class="message">
        We hope this email finds you well. We noticed that it's been a while since you last used Mitt Arv, and we wanted
        to reach out and invite you back. We know life can get busy, and sometimes it's easy to forget about apps we
        haven't used in a while.<br><br>

        But we wanted to remind you that by using Mitt Arv, you're not just taking advantage of great features and
        exclusive offers - you're also creating a lasting legacy. Whether you're sharing your thoughts and experiences
        with others using Emotional Will or Listing down Assets for your loved ones; every interaction helps build a
        record of your life that you can be proud of. So why not come back to Mitt Arv today and continue building your
        legacy?
        <br /> <br />
        We hope to see you back very soon on Mitt Arv :)

      </p>
      <button class="button">
          <a
            href="{{redirectUrl}}"
            target="_blank"
            style="color:white;font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;font-weight:400;font-size:12px;letter-spacing: 1.5%;margin: auto; text-decoration:none"
          >
            Open App
          </a>
        </button>
      <div class="intimation">
      </div>
      <p
        style="font-size: 12px;font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;color:white;font-weight:400;letter-spacing: 1.5%;text-align: center;">
        Best,<br>Team<span
          style=" font-size: 12px;font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: #84B5D2;font-weight: 700;letter-spacing: 1.5%;">
          Mitt
          Arv</span><br>
          <b>Zero - Life - Infinity</b>
      </p>
      <hr
        style="height:2px;border-width:0;color:#033348;background-color:#033348;margin-top:2.5%;margin-bottom:2.5%;width:110%;margin-left: -5%;">
        <p style="text-align: center;font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;font-size: 12px;color: white;letter-spacing: 1.5%;">
          For any inquiries, kindly reach out to us at<br> support@mittarv.com

      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>